        public java.util.List<java.lang.Double> prePerform(Chara source,
                                                   java.util.List<Chara> target,

        Called for the selected action of every character on every turn.

        Will go through the sources and targets(list) items and call perform() on them Lastly calls perform() on this action, which returns a list of damage values done by the action (one value per target)

        Parameters:

        target - the target charas
